01:04:43.220 --> 01:04:48.080
in Shanghai or Chongqing who
has just bought his first car.

01:04:48.080 --> 01:04:55.280
Chinese car ownership is
where ours was back in 1918.

01:04:55.280 --> 01:04:57.470
I forswear and who's
positively itching

01:04:57.470 --> 01:05:00.200
